---
// FAQ Section
---

<section class="faq-section" id="faq" data-fade-in>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-container">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How does the license key work?</summary>
        <p>Enter your license key in Mellon settings on first launch. The app validates it with our servers (requires internet once), then stores it securely in your macOS Keychain. Works offline forever after initial activation.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What if I want to use more than 3 devices?</summary>
        <p>Contact us at support@mellonvoice.com. We can discuss custom licensing for special cases like teams or educational institutions.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I upgrade from Single to Duo later?</summary>
        <p>Yes! Email your receipt to support@mellonvoice.com and we'll provide an upgrade path with credit for your original purchase.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What happens after the free update period ends?</summary>
        <p>Your app continues to work forever. Updates are optional—you can stay on your current version indefinitely. Optional update subscriptions available at $8-10/year if you want continued updates.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is there a refund policy?</summary>
        <p>30-day money-back guarantee through Gumroad. If you're not satisfied, contact Gumroad for a full refund, no questions asked.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Which macOS versions are supported?</summary>
        <p>Mellon works on macOS 12 (Monterey) and newer. We recommend running the latest macOS version for the best experience.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How is this different from built-in macOS dictation?</summary>
        <p>Mellon offers faster processing, better accuracy, custom shortcuts, and works universally across all apps. Plus, everything stays completely local with no Apple cloud processing.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you support languages other than English?</summary>
        <p>Currently, Mellon supports English with high accuracy. We're working on adding support for Spanish, French, and German in future updates.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ========== FAQ SECTION ========== */
  .faq-section {
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .faq-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: var(--space-3xl) auto 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-gray-300);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-subtle);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-size: 16px;
    outline: none;
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::before {
    content: '▶';
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: var(--space-sm);
    transition: transform var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::before {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>

